<Speech gate:gateId="160141" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="158824" majorType="ParlmemberSpeechStart"><Parlmember gate:gateId="156541" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<SpeechStart gate:gateId="158007" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="157478" majorType="speaker">Ιωάννης Δριβελέγκας</Chairman>):</SpeechStart></SpeechStart> Γιατί φωνάζετε, κυρία Μακρή; Δεν σας ακούει κανείς.</Speech> 
