<Speech gate:gateId="160143" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="158826" majorType="ParlmemberSpeechStart"><Parlmember gate:gateId="156543" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<SpeechStart gate:gateId="158008" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="157479" majorType="speaker">Ιωάννης Δριβελέγκας</Chairman>):</SpeechStart></SpeechStart> Δεν πειράζει; Έτσι, να μιλάμε; Ωραία, να το κάνουμε χάβρα.</Speech> 
<Speech gate:gateId="160144" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="158827" majorType="ParlmemberSpeechStart"><Parlmember gate:gateId="156544" majorType="speaker">ΡΑΧΗΛ ΜΑΚΡΗ</Parlmember>:</SpeechStart> Δεν πειράζει. Το ξέρει ο Υπουργός.</Speech> 
<Speech gate:gateId="160145" majorType="ParlmemberSpeech"><SpeechStart gate:gateId="158828" majorType="ParlmemberSpeechStart"><Parlmember gate:gateId="156545" majorType="speaker">ΠΡΟΕΔΡΕΥΩΝ</Parlmember> (<SpeechStart gate:gateId="158009" majorType="ChairmanSpeechStart"><Chairman gate:gateId="157480" majorType="speaker">Ιωάννης Δριβελέγκας</Chairman>):</SpeechStart></SpeechStart> Κύριε Υπουργέ, αυτά τα είχαμε συζητήσει.</Speech> 
